Now I'm not agreeing with everything the Church has done, nor are they perfect, or are their leaders perfect.  I am saying though that when a common belief has lasted this long without people finding a huge fualt in it (kinda hard when the Church uses that lame &quot;God works in mysterious ways&quot; excuse which i think is what Verant's &quot;The Vision&quot; was based on) that there must be something more to it than we can comprehend.<br>
